snippet.title: Clash Of Puppets - PC Steam Trailer
snippet.description:
Clash of Puppets - PC version for Steam

A B-Movie inspired Dual-Stick Hack'n'Slash Platformer from Drakkar Dev

Help Charlie getting out of his nightmares through 30 levels full of puppet-monsters inspired by classical B-movie genre.

Enjoy infinite gameplay playing the survival mode!
